## How to Embed Power BI Dashboard on a Website

If embedding the dashboard on your personal website or blog, use this iframe snippet:

```html
<iframe
  width="900"
  height="700"
  src="https://app.powerbi.com/view?r=your_report_embed_url"
  frameborder="0"
  allowFullScreen="true">
</iframe>
